{
  "stem": "20710.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were the ones that, they were just awful.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we were-- they were the militia, police, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they, you know, had the-- the authority over us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they were just terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They used to come and they used to-- to beat us up.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They used to take us, you know, to forced labor every day and take us out in-- in the fields there and dig ditches.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they used to stay with-- with rifles, and used to have fun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they used to, you know, shoot in the air and they used to.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And-- and we had to stay and dig ditches there from-- from about 8 o'clock in the morning till 6 o'clock in the evening.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And this was just the beginning when they just marched in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And this was going on until it got cold, you know.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I remember it was during the High Holidays.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I remember Erev Yom Kippur, we-- we came home, you know, after digging these ditches and not much to eat.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then, you know, also we made up, you know, sort of like to pray, to-- to fast like two-- two days a week, we used to fast.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Monday and Thursday we used to fast just for God to perform some miracles for us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But being young, sometimes I just wonder how things, you know, being young.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "It seems that the power of-- of-- when you're frightened, you want to live, you know, that I guess it's mind over matter.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "You get strong and, you know, even nothing to eat and nothing to-- I mean, very little.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But somehow, we pulled through.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And this was going on until it got deep into the fall.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
